  "synopsis": "The Konica Minolta \"Tenkuu\" Planetarium in Tokyo Skytree Town will run a Chibi Maruko-chan planetarium show from July 18 to August 31. The show, titled \"Planetarium Chibi Maruko-chan, Hoshi ni Negai wo\" (Planetarium Chibi Maruko-chan, Wish Upon a Star), celebrates the 25th anniversary of the Chibi Maruko-chan anime since it first aired in January 1990.\n(Source: ANN)",
